  "title": "Counter Service | Part Time | Training Provided | Up To $2K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Counter Service Crew (Part Time)</strong></p><p><strong>Working Location, Work Timing & Salary:</strong> <br /><br /><strong>One Raffles Place</strong><br />7.30am - 2.30pm (Mon - Fri)<br />$ 1700, 30 mins break</p><p><strong>Changi Business Park</strong><br />7am - 3pm (Mon - Fri)<br />$ 2000, 30 mins break<br /><br /><strong>Fusionopolis</strong><br />10.30am - 2.30pm (Mon - Thurs)<br />$ 800, no break<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle day-to-day operations according to SOP</li><li>Provide friendly customer service</li><li>Plating food for counter service</li><li>Cooking and mixing rice</li><li>Kitchen preparation work and mise en place</li><li>Stock-taking</li><li>Replenishing required ingredients</li><li>Cleaning and washing all used service / kitchen tools, equipment and workstations</li><li>Sweeping and mopping<br /> </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Training provided</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
